<h2 id="procedure">Procedure</h2>

<ol>
  <li>Lecture: What is AJAX</li>
  <li>Lecture: How does it work with JavaScript</li>
  <li>Lecture: How does it work with jQuery</li>
  <li>Diagram: Overall structure of the app</li>
  <li>Add GET example</li>
  <li>Add POST example</li>
  <li>Workshop 1</li>
  <li>Workshop Review</li>
  <li>Add DELETE example</li>
  <li>Workshop 2</li>
  <li>Workshop Review</li>
</ol>

<h2 id="workshops">Workshops</h2>

<h3 id="workshop-1-refresh">Workshop 1: Refresh</h3>

<ol>
  <li>Right now, you have to reload the page to get the new posts. Can you modify your app so that the posts are reloaded when you click a button?</li>
  <li>Right now, there is some duplication when we render the template, can you refactor?</li>
</ol>

<h3 id="workshop-2-polling--put">Workshop 2: Polling &amp; PUT</h3>

<ol>
  <li>Right now, you have to click on a button to refresh the feed. Can you check the server every 5 seconds to see if there are any new posts?</li>
  <li>Can you implement a PUT option to modify the data via AJAX?</li>
</ol>

